Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.65,0:23:23.11,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}做想做的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:50.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}空想戀愛主義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:01:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這些是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年穿的玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便說男裝是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女裝是內田的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.83,0:02:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到日本人就不能不提和服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.16,0:02:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到新年就不能不提正裝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.35,0:02:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是日本的常識
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們為了即將到來的新年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要舉行一次綵排
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綵排？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綵排？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  穿上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼華美的衣服穿我身上可使不得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我身上可是有著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這套服飾掩飾不了的大和之魂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好合適
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  接下來是冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這樣行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝等竟不見此繽紛之落櫻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣派倒是夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在你有更需要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廉恥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  內田？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人不禁懊悔為什麼沒能有一個不同的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某種較好的意義上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人不禁懊悔為什麼沒能有一個不同的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某種不好的意義上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好的意義？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香一定會說你很可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐會這樣說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下就可以迎接新年了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  吉野  挺晚的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱這兒已經滿是正月的氛圍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倆的衣服都挺合適呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩兒穿和服的時候不是要脫去內衣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得媽媽是這麼告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是穿和服的禮法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香一定會說你很可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會說你很可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別攔著我  內田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按禮法是要脫去內衣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是禮法也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:48.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來阿珍身上那和服是內田的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑一句話就能把氣氛弄得這麼有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:04:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩下子嘛  吉野
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快些打給藤岡君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還…還…還…還需要心理準備…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想邀他一同去參拜神社吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:16.99,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（註：原文初詣，指新年第一次參拜神社）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快點兒打去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好就有人預約了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.07,0:05:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預約？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家還有家人啦足球部的隊友之類吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  藤岡君的電話號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  是我的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同學她正在通話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再練習一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我是藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同學她在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香和千秋不也是「南同學」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈同學她在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用「同學」這倆字或許太古板了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp-22}　{\fsp1}League Champion{\r}\N聯賽冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.62,0:06:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:46.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（註：二者音似）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏…夏…夏…夏…夏奈…親
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說「夏奈同學」算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:00.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（重撥）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為期末考試得了滿分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以家裏給你買手機了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看錯你了  圭子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為至少你不會是這副德性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是什麼意…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確實比別人更擅長學習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次問到分數的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是笑著說「滿分」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不是「總是笑著說」…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  滿分這一點你不否定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊  圭子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂滿分是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂滿分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們這些學生來說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無可替代的榮耀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有那麼誇張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是圭子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你考滿分卻買了手機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為手機購買慾你把一百分這種榮耀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把學生之魂給出賣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是骯髒的滿分！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子在和誰打電話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在通話中…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在通話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是聽筒沒放好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機這玩意兒還挺方便的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:09:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不留神的話電話費開銷可不小…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機話費
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這玩意兒很貴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打太久的話也不會很貴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過說來這電話打得也夠長的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經四點了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多說了兩個小時了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個小時？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話費很貴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你打來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以話費會算在你那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別瞎扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這骯髒的滿分混賬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骯髒的…滿分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定只有我打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他拒絕接聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許就該在放寒假前約她的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去神社就可以見到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你打了很長時間電話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不許打那麼久哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐這好不容易操持家庭生計的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別再給她添亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話費的話問圭子拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是地址
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:47.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪的妄想\N模擬場景\N～豪華客船上的除夕篇～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前來伴您左右
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這碗天婦羅面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（註：炸魚蝦外裹麵粉的日式傳統食品）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃方便麵就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除夕的鐘聲還沒敲響哦  女兒們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏樹君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你帶來打工的那位保阪君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要自顧自地做面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了他心愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:13:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我不是問這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還需要其他理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來進展不錯啊  學長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夏樹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你給我介紹這麼一家不錯的店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏  能幫上忙我十分榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  做出讓您自己滿意的面了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你嘗嘗看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴隨入口而穿過鼻腔的那股
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醇厚而又不失清冽的芳香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需一口就彷彿親眼見到了學長烹飪時的風姿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼雄辯的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是學長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六成…不  得有七八成吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了蕎麥粉還加了小麥粉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以學長的廚藝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:14:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便不用小麥粉也能做出面來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告訴我理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用小麥粉確實是原汁原味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一絲瑕疵的完美味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會給人帶來極度的緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為飲食應該是安神養心的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而她也會是這麼想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得我的想法很幼稚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那並不是幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是溫情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.87,0:14:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要上哪兒去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長  祝您出師大捷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:52.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師和二宮同學\N最終話10小時特別篇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:15:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你忘記我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼傻話  二宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  上我這兒來  二宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  車子已經開走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宮同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是個假人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:25.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（註：第一句純粹是為了韻律，本意為"最開始出石頭"）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你們的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～  多謝多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好沉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進口的高級果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝到天亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未成年人可不能飲酒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水學姐  歡迎歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看二宮同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看肌肉男吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候去神社呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等真希她們來了再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淨是些看上去就稀奇古怪的果汁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碳酸飲料的話千秋會喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們先開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那麼各位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年來辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…水！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這果汁怎麼回事兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是進口貨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進口貨？但這味道怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廚房裏有一大堆顏色扎眼  一看就很可疑的果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:51.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊衝啊  兜襠布假面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:55.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了  兜襠布飛腿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊  最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:16:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣幹掉他  就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:00.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  鮮紅的血色兜襠布
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:02.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯規的攻擊方式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:05.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用兜襠布勒人脖子實在太卑劣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃快逃  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在第一回合結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香把左手放到藍色圓內
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手放到藍色圓內？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆都輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛…剛才那都是因為夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用英語道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.15,0:17:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了的二位請脫掉衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者請喝果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  拿出相機來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用來留下有趣的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  遊戲這才開始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式規則可是五局三分制
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:08.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（註：一種拳擊規則，比賽五局，每局三分鐘）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:15.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙方都絲毫沒有退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:17.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於迎來了最後一個回合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.75,0:18:20.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是了不得的戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左邊再多些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左邊再多些力道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大半夜的給我安靜點兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倆是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很可怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像惡魔一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:54.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  姐姐在哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你對面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能把春香和千秋整成這副德性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很好喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是高級貨色嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那兩位睡會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp40}　{\fsp1}Twin Star Game{\r}\N老闆  給二位準備雙子星遊戲和這種飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當真是真的好喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是果汁嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去神社的人請舉手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夥兒都倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像做得有些過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.81,0:20:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱倆去個好地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人才是最不正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐  其實那果汁很難喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是進口貨嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直強忍著喝下去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是高級貨色嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然需要強忍就別喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是我付的帳嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們終於結婚了啊  二宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千…千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.09,0:21:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家到底在哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一定在某盞燈火之下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,側耳傾聽著這除夕的鐘聲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就足夠了
